  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a blender, combine charred Thai chili paste, herbal Indian-style yoghurt, lime juice, ginger, cumin, coriander, and salt.",
    "3. Add the fish fillets to the marinade and mix well.",
    "4. Grill the fish for 4-5 minutes per side or until cooked through.",
